      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. I've babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition, inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
