    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 911 Turbo is a superlative example featuring the legendary Mezger-designed 3.6L flat-six. The powerplant utilizes a true dry-sump lubrication system and twin BorgWarner K16 turbochargers, delivering linear boost with zero weeping at the rear main seal or turbo seals. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise gate entry, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a fully functional AWD viscous coupling. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, supported by original Bilstein damping and pristine bushings. A recent DME readout confirms zero overrev ignitions in higher ranges, and the paint depth readings are consistent across all panels. This is a mechanically turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
